; Regression test for issue #779: Please add pricrdb entries in both directions (BZ#779)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/779
; The request is that pricedb command output entries in both forward and reverse directions,
; so that the generated pricedb file can be used for conversions in either direction.
; Currently only the forward direction (EUR -> USD) is output, not the reverse (USD -> EUR).

P 2024/01/01 EUR 1.20 USD

2024/01/01 Test
    Assets:EUR   100 EUR @ 1.20 USD
    Assets:Cash   -120 USD

test pricedb
P 2024/01/01 00:00:00 EUR 1.20 USD
end test
